  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Home to some of Europe's most iconic peaks, France and Switzerland make for a fantastic multi-centre holiday with plenty of walking and dramatic landscapes</h2>
<p>Start your stay in the famous resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, moving on to <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> via the picturesque Mont Blanc Express railway journey. For an extended stay, continue on to <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a> in the Bernese Oberland and explore two or three famous resorts in awe-inspiring settings linked by beautiful rail journeys across the Alps.</p>
<h2>Your multi-centre holiday options:</h2>
<ul>
<li>The option of 4, 7, 10, 11 or 14 nights accommodation in your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Travel and change destination on a Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
<h2>Your holiday includes:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in your first destination, between destinations (train transfer) and from your hotel in your second (or third) destination to the airport by train transfer</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
<li>Free Chamonix Guest Card with discounted attractions, up to 50% discounts on Chamonix Mobility bus tickets and free travel on the Mont Blanc Express (exclusions apply)</li>
<li>Swiss Half Fare Card - worth over £100 – included as part of your Swiss rail tickets</li>
<li>Up to two included guided walks per person per week when staying on selected days in Chamonix, Zermatt and Grindelwald (walks operate on selected days only and are subject to availability)</li>
</ul>
