  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Chamonix</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/db03040b91a34a5c9efdc1d724335bf4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/db03040b91a34a5c9efdc1d724335bf4}" title="Hotel Lykke">Hotel Lykke</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13103488/hotel-lykke-classic-double-room.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Lykke" data-udi="umb://media/55baee30d9ba4e61aebd2ca29c378301" /></p>
<p>Positioned near the centre of Chamonix, the Hotel Lykke is a great option, with a welcoming atmosphere and with it’s recent renovation, the hotel has modern facilities including a spa area which includes an indoor pool.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/36990e5325fe4ddc9065bff1984dbeb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/36990e5325fe4ddc9065bff1984dbeb0}" title="Refuge des Aiglons">Refuge des Aiglons</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13082505/refuge_des_aiglons_terrassetemmos-2_39321265582_o.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Refuge des Aiglons" data-udi="umb://media/39fcf586ff554f40bf64d78f9f675fbb" /></p>
<p>Positioned on the edge of Chamonix and with an outdoor swimming pool and restaurant terrace, the Refuge des Aiglons is a great option, with family friendly facilities to enjoy.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/83040257fea44fbea7942a48629cc9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/83040257fea44fbea7942a48629cc9cb}" title="Hotel Alpina">Hotel Alpina</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13086023/alpina-facade-1_4-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.0095923261391" alt="Hotel Alpina" data-udi="umb://media/efef678c1a9f40b4b5fabf60fe86276f" /></p>
<p>Hotel Alpina is a modern hotel in the centre of Chamonix, it makes a great base to explore all the walking trails on offer and there's a bus stop across the road from the hotel so it's easy to connect to nearby areas.</p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Zermatt</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068}" title="Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa">Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104685/le-mirabeau-garten-_-haupthaus.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ed440d94eb384a25ae913d75e3711b96" /></p>
<p>The Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa makes for the perfect mountain get-away. This elegant hotel is popular with guests who return year after year. Spend some time in the Alpine Hideaway Spa, treat yourself to a drink in Marie's Deli, or spend some time in the garden.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f}" title="Hotel Alex">Hotel Alex</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104686/wellness_whirlpool-030-lowres.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/94a8255dc66943a48a2ab979b1550ef6" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Alex, with it's impressive décor, impeccable service and excellent wellness facilities, makes a great choice. Situated close to the train station and Gornergrat mountain railway, it makes an excellent base to explore all the local area has to offer. </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View All Hotels in Zermatt</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<h2>Hotels in Grindelwald</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/429056524d9645e4aee65666e7fe7e2c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/429056524d9645e4aee65666e7fe7e2c}" title="Hotel Eiger">Eiger Mountain &amp; Soul Resort</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104684/doppelzimmer-lifestyle-chic.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/cb4f2ae9324a4d04b178a167d3713388" />With a great location in Grindelwald, the Eiger Mountain &amp; Soul Resort makes a great base to explore the area. You're positioned close to the Grindelwald First gondola and after a day of discovering the area, the hotel's spa facilities are a welcome treat.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb}" title="Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof">Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104683/hotel-summer_web.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/38ce616753784b9a9dcc780f501774ea" /></p>
<p>Discover the local area but also take the time to relax and enjoy the luxury spa facilities at the Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof. With delicious food to tuck into as well as a great location, just two minutes' walk from the train station, this hotel makes for a great stay.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View All Hotels in Grindelwald</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
